<header class="modal-header">
    <h1>您确定要删除此用户?</h1>
</header>
<a class="close icon-x" href="" title="Close" {{action "closeModal"}}><span class="hidden">Close</span></a>

<div class="modal-body">
  {{#if user.count.posts}}
      <strong>警告:</strong> <span class="red">此用户是{{pluralize user.count.posts 'post'}}的作者.</span> 所有帖子和用户数据都将被删除. 没有办法恢复这个.
  {{else}}
      <strong>警告:</strong> 所有用户数据将被删除. 没有办法恢复这个.
  {{/if}}
</div>

<div class="modal-footer">
    <button {{action "closeModal"}} class="btn btn-default btn-minor">取消</button>
    {{#gh-spin-button action="confirm" class="btn btn-red" submitting=submitting}}删除{{/gh-spin-button}}
</div>
